  "2026-07-11T11:10:40.136Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Duplicate-check evidence 2026-07-11: pm context, list-open, list-in-progress, and all-status searches for native codex plugin, pm-codex Apps SDK, ChatGPT Codex plugin official docs, Codex plugin npx fallback cache, and native ChatGPT plugin found the closed shipped lineage pm-0c9q/pm-d97r plus Claude-only pm-l9wl/pm-dudr, but no item covering current OpenAI plugin and Apps SDK alignment. This feature extends rather than reopens the completed May implementation."
